description: MEH Diamond Pass NFT is a special acknowledgment to the steadfast supporters of the $MEH community. Limited to just 258 NFTs, this exclusive variant is awarded to those who held over 1,000,000 $MEH in their wallets, as recognized in a dedicated blockchain snapshot. While offering the same utility as the MEH Default Pass, the Diamond version also serves as a gesture of gratitude, celebrating your significant contribution to the community's growth and success.
name: MEH Diamond Pass #209
